The paper proposes a novel algorithm for credit assignment in recurrent neural networks, which is a common topic in machine learning and artificial intelligence (cs.LG, cs.AI, cs.NE). The algorithm involves a learned attention mechanism, which is a common technique in natural language processing and computer vision (cs.CL, cs.CV). Therefore, the most likely categories are cs.LG, cs.AI, and cs.NE, followed by cs.CL and cs.CV.
